response.overview: The evil warlord, Dr.Skull, is ready for world domination. Only two martial artists of the Booticus McMaximus squad stand in the way of his army and loyal assassins. Can they succeed? Or will the eccentric dark lord rule the planet?
response.tagline: War is upon us - the evil warlord Dr Skull has prepared an army to attack the forces of the united World Alliance and their general.
response.title: Skull Wars
